Fly from planet to planet and pick up aliens (Hoopsies) spread through the endless galaxy. You need to make breathtaking curves between planets to pick up as many aliens as you can before you hit an asteroid and damage your UFO.

▶ UPO is simple to learn, but difficult to master!

Rescue more aliens and be the FIRST among your Facebook or Google+ friends!


HOW TO PLAY

•  Tap a planet where do you want your UFO to go;
•  Dodge asteroids;
•  Pick aliens from planets;
•  Catch power-up aliens on the fly;
•  Every saved alien = +1;
•  Every alien left behind = -1;
•  Game ends when you damage your UFO;


HIGHLIGHTS

•  UPO is FREE;
•  Quick & simple to play;
•  Highly refined UFO flight physics;
•  Unlock UFO-s with better performance or stronger durability;
•  Funny alien characters and alien creatures;
•  Colorful environment with planets, stars and asteroids;
•  Funny music and sounds of alien characters;


FAQ

Q: What does UPO mean?
A: UPO = Unidentified Picking Object


Play UPO and enjoy your flight!


